cuisine.title: Cuisine
cuisine.text: At Unicorn, fusion cuisine is king. Our chef skillfully blends Mediterranean influences with Asian touches to create dishes that are as visually stunning as they are tasty. From the freshness of local products to exotic spices, each bite tells a story of travel and discovery. Discover a creative menu where grilled fish rubs shoulders with reinvented sushi and fragrant mezzes, for a unique taste experience in Calvi.
